    "Tokenization is a way of cutting a string of text into discrete chunks, chosen to be statistically efficient.",
    "In many tokenization schemes, one token corresponds to roughly three-quarters of an English word.",
    "ChatGPT became available to logged-out users in April 2024, i.e., users could use ChatGPT without signing up for an account with an email address.",
